-- Tests for repaying borrows

Macro SetupBorrow borrowRate
    NewComptroller price:1.0 -- TODO: This should really be a price for a specific asset
    ListedOToken ZRX oZRX borrowRate
    ListedEtherToken oETH borrowRate 0.005e9
    SetCollateralFactor oZRX collateralFactor:0.5
    SetCollateralFactor oETH collateralFactor:0.5
    Donate oETH 0.003e18
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX oZRX
    Mint Geoff 100e18 oZRX
    EnterMarkets Geoff oZRX oETH

Macro NewBorrowEth borrowAmount borrowRate
    SetupBorrow borrowRate
    Borrow Geoff borrowAmount oETH

Test "Borrow, hold a few blocks, and repay part"
    NewBorrowEth borrowAmount:0.001e18 borrowRate:0.000005
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH BorrowBalance Geoff) 0.001e18
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH TotalBorrowsCurrent) 0.001e18
    -- Now let's add some blocks and see what happs
    FastForward 300000 Blocks -- 0.001e18 * (1 + 300000 * 0.000005)
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH BorrowBalance Geoff) 0.0025e18
    -- Now let's repay one full token
    Expect Changes (EtherBalance Geoff) -0.001e18
    Expect Changes (EtherBalance oETH) +0.001e18
    RepayBorrowEth Geoff 0.001e18 oETH
    ---- Let's check the overall numbers
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH BorrowBalance Geoff) 0.0015e18
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH TotalBorrowsCurrent) 0.0015e18
    FastForward 200000 Blocks -- 0.0015e18 * (1 + 2000 * 0.000005)
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH BorrowBalance Geoff) 0.003e18
    Assert Equal (OToken oETH TotalBorrowsCurrent) 0.003e18

